{"type": "article", "id": 26642, "title": "餐具系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-11T06:44:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171511MYFseJi1j4WgyCE9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">第一眼看到 Evoke 系列餐具，你也许很容易联想到原始社会的人们用贝壳制作的工具。设计师 <a href=\"http://www.sarahlindaforrer.com/\">Sarah-Linda Forre</a> 希望通过这些看起来非常原生态的器具，挑战用刀叉的传统用餐方式，激起人们对于食物的思考。目前这套餐具还处于开发阶段，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.voordekunst.nl/projecten/4449-evoke-een-collectie-eetgereedschap-1\">链接</a>参与众筹。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171509GUSl5QgR4iosmvca.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.92298289\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171510C9DWBc5uezLP2kOt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021715105reMUbktHXPC4GnT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171511M9YDdgqnS7IcJAOy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}